            <title>[LUCENE-2619] simple improvements to tests</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2619</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Simon had requested some docs on what all our test options do, so lets clean it up and doc it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;i propose:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;change all vars to be tests.xxx (e.g. tests.threadspercpu, tests.multiplier, ...)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;ensure all 6 build systems (lucene, solr, each solr contrib) respect these.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;add a simple wiki page listing what these do.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</description>
